description:
This is a 48 minute workout called '45 Minute HIIT Tabata Workout with Weights - HIIT Workouts for Weight Loss & Strength at Home' from the channel HASfit.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.
